title: Your Kid's Next Science Project

  • 1 Beaker

The Micro Flat Twisted Bracelet blends precision with fluidity‚Äîsleek, low-key, and unapologetically sharp. Its twisted design adds quiet movement and texture, perfect for those who speak volumes without saying a word. Whether worn solo or stacked, it delivers timeless edge. Waterproof and anti-tarnish, it‚Äôs built to keep up‚Äîand never fade.

At GRYTT, we don‚Äôt mess around with our materials. Our jewelry is crafted from solid Recycled 316L Grade Stainless Steel with an 18K Gold or Rhodium Plating, using PVD technology. Translation: it‚Äôs tougher than your average bling and built to last.

This stuff will stand the test of time, just like you. It‚Äôs easy to keep clean, hypoallergenic (so no itchy skin), and best of all‚Äîno more worrying about green fingers. We‚Äôre in the business of looking good, not turning you into the Hulk.

Waterproof? Yes. Sturdy? Definitely. This jewelry is made for your everyday grind.*

Maintenance? Simple. Just grab a cloth, hit it with a little warm water and mild soap, give it a gentle rub-down, rinse, and dry. Easy, right? Keep it sharp without breaking a sweat.

*The links or jump rings connecting the hook in chains & bracelets are too thin to effectively sustain 18K gold plating. However, the main part of the bracelet will be fully waterproof and won‚Äôt pose any issues. The bracelet is held by the jump rings or links during the 18K gold dipping process, which makes it difficult for the plating to adhere strongly to those specific areas. We recommend you keep the jump rings on 18K Gold Plated chains & bracelet away from water, harsh chemicals & sweat.
